{
  "question_id": "41d34b41-12af-4afa-b138-e7e757f37474",
  "short_text": "Hollow Square - 2",
  "content": "Given a number `N`, write a program that prints a **Hollow Square** of `N + 2` rows using pluses (`+`), hyphens (`-`), and pipes (`|`) . The first and last row contain pluses(`+`) and hyphens(`-`), and the middle rows contain pipes(`|`) as shown below.\r\n\r\n```\r\n+ - - - +\r\n|       |\r\n|       |\r\n|       |\r\n+ - - - +\r\n```\r\n\r\n<MultiLineNote>\r\nThere is a space after every character.\r\n</MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n#### Input\r\n\r\nThe input will be a single line containing an integer representing `N`.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n#### Output\r\n\r\nThe output should be `N + 2` lines containing pluses (`+`), hyphens (`-`) and pipes (`|`) as a **Hollow Square** shown in the sample output.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n#### Explanation\r\n\r\nFor example, if the given number is `N = 5`,\r\n\r\n- The **Hollow Square** should contain **7** lines. (`5 + 2 = 7`)\r\n- The first and last lines should contain **2** pluses (`+`) and **5** hyphens (`-`), as shown below.\r\n\r\n```\r\n+ - - - - - +\r\n```\r\n\r\n- The middle **5** lines should contain two pipes (`|`) with **10** spaces between them, as shown below.\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n|           |\r\n|           |\r\n|           |\r\n|           |\r\n|           |\r\n```\r\n\r\n- The final **Hollow Square** is as shown in the given image.\r\n\r\n<Img imageSrc='https://res.cloudinary.com/dqqdcnmqn/image/upload/v1672229085/Screenshot_from_2022-12-28_17-34-23_ecgjtl.png' widthPercent='70'/>\r\n\r\n<MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\nIn the given image,\r\n\r\n- The Empty box indicates two spaces (\"&nbsp;&nbsp;\").\r\n- The Plus in the box indicates a plus and a space (\"+ \").\r\n- The Hyphen in the box indicates a hyphen and a space (\"- \").\r\n- The Pipe in the box indicates a pipe and a space (\"| \").\r\n  </MultiLineNote>\r\n\r\nThe output should be,\r\n\r\n```\r\n+ - - - - - +\r\n|           |\r\n|           |\r\n|           |\r\n|           |\r\n|           |\r\n+ - - - - - +\r\n```",
  "question_type": "CODING",
  "content_type": "MARKDOWN",
  "codes": [
    {
      "code_id": "e6dce586-0d73-447a-8a64-f13fc7fdf4a4",
      "code_content": "n = int(input())\n\nhyphens = \"- \" * n\nfirst_row = \"+ \" + hyphens + \"+\"\nlast_row = \"+ \" + hyphens + \"+\"\n\nprint(first_row)\n\nfor row in range(n):\n    spaces = \"  \" * n\n    each_row = \"| \" + spaces + \"|\"\n    \n    print(each_row)\n    \n\nprint(last_row)",
